claim.claim-text:
1. An oral composition comprising: 
a. an effective amount of one or more linear polyphosphates having an average chain length of about 4 or more; 
b. from about 0.15% to about 5% of a fluoride ion source; 
c. from about 0.1% to about 15% of a stannous ion source; 
d. an effective amount of a buffering agent; 
e. from about 6% to about 70% of an abrasive polishing material containing less than 23% calcium; and 
f. from about 50% to about 99% of one or more aqueous carriers; 
wherein the oral composition has a total water content of from about 1% to about 20%.
